*[[泡碱|泡碱]] Na<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub>·10(H<sub>2</sub>O)
*[[碳钙铀矿|碳钙铀矿]] Ca(UO<sub>2</sub>)(CO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·5(H<sub>2</sub>O)

